[{"id": 520882, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3470, "text": "Alif lam meem."}, {"id": 520883, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3471, "text": "DETTA \u00c4R budskap ur den uppenbarade Skriften, ur vilken visdom,"}, {"id": 520602, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3472, "text": "v\u00e4gledning och n\u00e5d [fl\u00f6dar] \u00f6ver dem som g\u00f6r det goda och det r\u00e4tta,"}, {"id": 520860, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3473, "text": "de som f\u00f6rr\u00e4ttar b\u00f6nen och hj\u00e4lper de beh\u00f6vande; det \u00e4r dessa som har f\u00f6rvissningen att det eviga livet [v\u00e4ntar]."}, {"id": 520648, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3474, "text": "De f\u00f6ljer Guds v\u00e4gledning och dem skall det g\u00e5 v\u00e4l i h\u00e4nder."}, {"id": 520884, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3475, "text": "Men det finns m\u00e4nniskor som betalar [historieber\u00e4ttarna f\u00f6r deras] historier f\u00f6r att [med deras hj\u00e4lp], utan egen kunskap, locka [andra att avvika] fr\u00e5n Guds v\u00e4g, och som [f\u00f6rs\u00f6ker] g\u00f6ra narr av [dem som f\u00f6ljer] den. De skall f\u00e5 utst\u00e5 ett f\u00f6r\u00f6dmjukande straff."}, {"id": 520885, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3476, "text": "Och n\u00e4r V\u00e5ra budskap l\u00e4ses upp f\u00f6r [en s\u00e5dan man] v\u00e4nder han sig bort med \u00f6verl\u00e4gsen min och beter sig som om han inte hade h\u00f6rt, som om han varit d\u00f6v p\u00e5 b\u00e5da \u00f6ronen. L\u00e5t honom veta att ett pl\u00e5gsamt straff [v\u00e4ntar honom]."}, {"id": 520886, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3477, "text": "P\u00e5 dem som tror och lever r\u00e4ttskaffens v\u00e4ntar lycksalighetens lustg\u00e5rdar,"}, {"id": 520887, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3478, "text": "d\u00e4r de i enlighet med Guds l\u00f6fte skall f\u00f6rbli till evig tid; Han \u00e4r den Allsm\u00e4ktige, den Vise."}, {"id": 520888, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3479, "text": "Det \u00e4r Gud som har rest himlarna utan varje synligt st\u00f6d och Han har s\u00e4nkt ned i jorden fast f\u00f6rankrade berg, s\u00e5 att den inte svajar under er fot, och Han har l\u00e5tit djur av alla slag sprida sig \u00f6ver den. Och Vi l\u00e5ter regn falla fr\u00e5n skyn s\u00e5 att alla sorters nyttiga [v\u00e4xter] kan gro och spira p\u00e5 jorden."}, {"id": 520889, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 411, "ruku": 355, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3480, "text": "Detta \u00e4r Guds skapelse; visa Mig nu vad det \u00e4r som andra \u00e4n Han har skapat! - Nej, de or\u00e4ttf\u00e4rdiga har alldeles uppenbart g\u00e5tt vilse!"}, {"id": 520890, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3481, "text": "VI SK\u00c4NKTE Luqman visdom [och gav honom denna f\u00f6rmaning:] \"Var tacksam mot Gud [f\u00f6r Hans v\u00e4lg\u00e4rningar]. Den tacksamme har sj\u00e4lv gott av sin tacksamhet men den otacksamme [skall veta att] Gud \u00e4r Sig sj\u00e4lv nog och [att] allt lov och pris tillkommer Honom.\""}, {"id": 520891, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3482, "text": "Och Luqman talade till sin son och f\u00f6rmanade honom: \"K\u00e4re son! S\u00e4tt inte medhj\u00e4lpare vid Guds sida; att s\u00e4tta medhj\u00e4lpare vid Hans sida \u00e4r att beg\u00e5 en sv\u00e5r or\u00e4tt!"}, {"id": 520892, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3483, "text": "Gud har anbefallt m\u00e4nniskan [att visa] godhet mot sina f\u00f6r\u00e4ldrar; [hon b\u00f6r t\u00e4nka p\u00e5 att] modern har burit sitt barn genom det ena svaghetstillst\u00e5ndet efter det andra, [f\u00f6tt det] och ammat det under tv\u00e5 \u00e5r. Tacka Mig och dina f\u00f6r\u00e4ldrar [och minns att] Jag \u00e4r m\u00e5let f\u00f6r er f\u00e4rd!"}, {"id": 520893, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3484, "text": "Men om de vill f\u00f6rm\u00e5 dig att s\u00e4tta vid Min sida n\u00e5got som du st\u00e5r fr\u00e4mmande f\u00f6r, skall du inte lyda dem. Omge dem i detta liv som sig b\u00f6r [med dina \u00f6mma omsorger], och f\u00f6lj samma v\u00e4g som de som v\u00e4nder tillbaka till Mig i \u00e5nger [\u00f6ver sina synder]. Till Mig skall ni f\u00f6ras \u00e5ter och Jag skall l\u00e5ta er veta vad era handlingar [var v\u00e4rda]."}, {"id": 520894, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3485, "text": "K\u00e4re son! \u00c4ven om det [som du har gjort] v\u00e4ger s\u00e5 litet som ett senapskorn och [ligger dolt] i en klippa eller i himlarna eller i jorden, skall Gud l\u00e5ta det komma i dagen. Guds [v\u00e4gar] \u00e4r outgrundliga; Han genomsk\u00e5dar allt och \u00e4r underr\u00e4ttad om allt."}, {"id": 520895, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3486, "text": "K\u00e4re son! F\u00f6rr\u00e4tta b\u00f6nen och anbefall det som \u00e4r r\u00e4tt och f\u00f6rbjud det som \u00e4r or\u00e4tt. Och b\u00e4r med j\u00e4mnmod det [onda] som drabbar dig! Och st\u00e5 fast vid dina f\u00f6resatser!"}, {"id": 520896, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3487, "text": "Upptr\u00e4d aldrig med \u00f6verl\u00e4gsenhet mot [andra] och trampa inte denna jord med inbilsk h\u00f6gf\u00e4rd! Gud \u00e4r inte v\u00e4n till de \u00f6verl\u00e4gsna, de som vill vara f\u00f6rmer \u00e4n andra."}, {"id": 520897, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 412, "ruku": 356, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3488, "text": "Var m\u00e5ttfull i ditt beteende och d\u00e4mpa din r\u00f6st! Finns det n\u00e5got fulare \u00e4n \u00e5snans skriande?\""}, {"id": 520899, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3489, "text": "INSER NI inte att Gud har l\u00e5tit allt det som himlarna rymmer och det som jorden b\u00e4r tj\u00e4na er och att Han har \u00f6verhopat er med Sina g\u00e5vor b\u00e5de i det yttre och det inre? Men det finns de som tvistar om Gud utan vare sig kunskap eller v\u00e4gledning och utan [att lysas av] uppenbarelsens ljus."}, {"id": 520900, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 164, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3490, "text": "Och n\u00e4r dessa m\u00e4nniskor uppmanas att r\u00e4tta sig efter det som Gud har uppenbarat, s\u00e4ger de: \"Nej, vi f\u00f6ljer v\u00e5ra f\u00f6rf\u00e4ders v\u00e4g.\" Och om det var Dj\u00e4vulen sj\u00e4lv som hade uppmanat dem [att g\u00e5 raka v\u00e4gen] in i den flammande Elden?"}, {"id": 520901, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3491, "text": "Den som med hela sitt v\u00e4sen underkastar sig Guds vilja och som g\u00f6r det goda och det r\u00e4tta har vunnit ett s\u00e4kert f\u00e4ste. Allt g\u00e5r till sist upp till Gud."}, {"id": 520902, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3492, "text": "Men l\u00e5t inte ditt sinne tyngas av att [m\u00e4nniskor] f\u00f6rnekar sanningen! Till Oss skall de f\u00f6ras \u00e5ter och Vi skall l\u00e5ta dem veta vad deras handlingar [var v\u00e4rda]; Gud vet vad som r\u00f6r sig i m\u00e4nniskans innersta."}, {"id": 520903, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3493, "text": "Vi skall l\u00e5ta dem gl\u00e4djas en liten tid \u00e5t livet; d\u00e4refter skall Vi utl\u00e4mna dem \u00e5t ett tungt straff."}, {"id": 520904, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3494, "text": "OCH OM du fr\u00e5gar m\u00e4nniskorna: \"Vem har skapat himlarna och jorden?\" - svarar de helt s\u00e4kert: \"Gud.\" S\u00e4g: \"Gud ske lov och pris!\" Nej, de flesta av dem \u00e4r okunniga."}, {"id": 520905, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3495, "text": "Gud tillh\u00f6r allt i himlarna och p\u00e5 jorden. Gud \u00e4r Den som \u00e4r Sig sj\u00e4lv nog, Den som allt lov och pris tillkommer."}, {"id": 520906, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3496, "text": "Om \u00e4n jordens alla tr\u00e4d blev till pennor och havet, ut\u00f6kat med sju hav, blev till bl\u00e4ck skulle det inte r\u00e4cka f\u00f6r att skriva ned Guds ord. - Gud \u00e4r allsm\u00e4ktig, vis."}, {"id": 520907, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 413, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3497, "text": "Att skapa er alla och l\u00e5ta er uppst\u00e5 p\u00e5 nytt \u00e4r detsamma som [att skapa] en enda m\u00e4nniska [och l\u00e5ta henne \u00e5teruppst\u00e5]. Gud h\u00f6r allt, ser allt."}, {"id": 520908, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 414, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3498, "text": "Inser du inte att det \u00e4r Gud som l\u00e5ter natten glida in i dagen och dagen glida in i natten, och att Han har underordnat solen och m\u00e5nen under Sina lagar; de l\u00f6per var och en sitt [kretslopp] till en [av Honom] fastst\u00e4lld tidpunkt - och att Gud \u00e4r v\u00e4l underr\u00e4ttad om vad ni g\u00f6r"}, {"id": 520909, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 414, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3499, "text": "Detta, d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att Gud \u00e4r Sanningen, och allt det som m\u00e4nniskor anropar i Hans st\u00e4lle \u00e4r sken och l\u00f6gn; Gud \u00e4r den H\u00f6ge, den V\u00e4ldige."}, {"id": 520910, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 414, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3500, "text": "Ser du inte att Gud med Sin v\u00e4lsignelse l\u00e5ter skeppen segla \u00f6ver havet f\u00f6r att visa er n\u00e5gra av Sina tecken? I detta ligger f\u00f6rvisso budskap till var och en som st\u00e5r fast i motg\u00e5ngen och som tackar [Gud] i allt."}, {"id": 520911, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 414, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3501, "text": "N\u00e4r m\u00e4nniskorna [f\u00e4rdas p\u00e5 havet] och ser v\u00e5gorna h\u00e4va sig \u00f6ver dem som ett tak, anropar de Gud med ren och uppriktig tro, men n\u00e4r Han har f\u00f6rt dem [oskadda] i land f\u00f6rs\u00f6ker n\u00e5gra av dem g\u00e5 en v\u00e4g mellan tro och otro. Men bara den alltigenom falske, den som inte vet vad tacksamhet vill s\u00e4ga, avvisar V\u00e5ra budskap."}, {"id": 520912, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 414, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3502, "text": "M\u00c4NNISKOR! Frukta er Herre och b\u00e4va inf\u00f6r den Dag d\u00e5 en fader inte kan l\u00f6sk\u00f6pa sin son och en son inte kan \u00f6verl\u00e4mna sig som l\u00f6sen f\u00f6r sin fader! Guds l\u00f6fte \u00e4r sanning. L\u00e5t er d\u00e5 inte f\u00f6rledas av det jordiska livets [lockelser] och l\u00e5t inte Dj\u00e4vulen f\u00f6ra er bakom ljuset vad g\u00e4ller Guds [dom]."}, {"id": 520913, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 31, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0644\u0642\u0645\u0627\u0646", "surah_en_name": "Luqman", "surah_en_name_translation": "Luqman", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 21, "manzil": 5, "page": 414, "ruku": 357, "hizb_quarter": 165, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3503, "text": "Det \u00e4r Gud som har kunskap om den Yttersta stunden; det \u00e4r Han som l\u00e5ter regnet falla och Han som vet vad som ligger g\u00f6mt i moderlivet. Men ingen vet vad morgondagen b\u00e4r i sitt sk\u00f6te, och ingen vet var p\u00e5 denna jord han skall d\u00f6. Gud vet allt, \u00e4r underr\u00e4ttad om allt."}]